WEBVTT

00:02:57.554 --> 00:03:00.576
So there was a priest and a priestess.

00:03:00.600 --> 00:03:03.976
The priest was highly
revered in the village.

00:03:04.000 --> 00:03:08.176
Wherever he went, four people would
prostate there, five would prostate here.

00:03:08.200 --> 00:03:10.056
Everywhere people sang his praises,

00:03:10.080 --> 00:03:12.936
but the minute he would walk
into his home,

00:03:12.960 --> 00:03:14.960
the priestess would say, “So you’re back?”

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:17.877
The priest was very distressed.

00:03:17.901 --> 00:03:20.296
He wondered, “The entire
village is honouring me,

00:03:20.320 --> 00:03:22.336
people are falling at my feet

00:03:22.360 --> 00:03:25.616
but my wife, the priestess, doesn’t
consider me anything at all,

00:03:25.640 --> 00:03:27.976
she has absolutely no regard for me.

00:03:28.000 --> 00:03:30.280
Now the priest was an honorable man